 __________________________________________________________________________________________________
| Layer                  | Purpose                               | Technologies                    |
| -----------------------| --------------------------------------|---------------------------------|
| Frontend (Client Side) | What users see & interact with        | HTML, CSS, JavaScript           |
| Backend (Server Side)  | Processes data, logic, authentication | Python, Java, Node.js, C#, etc. |
| Database               | Stores data permanently               | MySQL, MongoDB, PostgreSQL      |
|__________________________________________________________________________________________________|